<p>If you are having problems with this site, please contact us by filling out <%= link_to 'this support form', 'http://nrs.harvard.edu/urn-3:hul.eother:edasupport' %>.</p>

<p>For permission to use images or transcriptions included on EDA, see our <%= link_to 'Copyright and Terms of Use', terms_path %> page.</p>

<p>To obtain higher resolution images than are provided by the <%= link_to 'download images', "#{about_path}#images" %> function in EDA, contact the library that owns the original manuscript. The name of the owning library is found in the image credits, and contact information is found under <%= link_to 'Partners & Credits', team_path %>.</p>

<p>For general information about Emily Dickinson, consult the <%= link_to 'FAQ', faq_path %> page and explore the <%= link_to 'Dickinson-Related Sites', "#{resources_path}#dickinson-related-sites" %> included in <%= link_to 'Resources', resources_path %>.</p>
